caption: "Vapor product"
created: 20260405120000000
modified: 20260405120000000
title: Policy1331(s1)(7)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

shall mean any product that employs a heating element, power source, electronic circuit or other electronic, chemical or mechanical means, regardless of shape or size, to produce a vapor that may or may not include nicotine or cannabis and is inhaled by the user of such product.
